<!-- 4.3.7 -->
<div class='toload proposition'>
	<p><span class='envidentifier'>Proposition 4.3.7</span>
	If $\alpha$ is an action of $S$ on an algebra $A$, then $\mathscr{N}(\alpha)$ is a two-sided ideal of $\mathscr{L}(\alpha)$.
	</p>
</div>